    "name": "Dreadful Night at School",
    "steam_appid": 3283680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283680/extras/a590e244867c303b0cd9a56e48e4ac2c.avif?t=1731064122\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>&quot;Dreadful Night at School&quot;</strong> – a <strong>dark thriller</strong> created by an RPG Maker fan, for all fans!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Imagine spending a night at school with a group of friends. Sounds like a great idea for fun, right? But as darkness falls, the atmosphere becomes a bit... unsettling. Suddenly, amidst fun and giggles, strange things are about to happen. One of your companions has sinister intentions, and the fun quickly turns into a terrifying events!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throughout the game, you will need to observe the characters behavior and try to uncover who is behind the dark crimes. The school, which was supposed to be a place of adventure, turns into a maze full of dangers. Escape? Well, it may not be that simple...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you manage to unmask the guilty one and escape the school, or will you end up as another victim in this  night adventure? Clues await, and the truth may be closer than it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3283680/extras/34391286c622e39c636baf0b00e5bccd.avif?t=1731064122\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One-night lenght:</strong> A game designed for a single evening session that you won't regret.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Graphics:</strong> Pixel art familiar from RPG Maker games, enhanced with beautiful lighting effects and original renders straight from Blender.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong> A narrative filled with twists and moments you won't forget for a long time. Will you manage to uncover who is responsible for the chaos faster than the others?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enjoyable Gameplay:</strong> The game is easy to complete without a walkthrough, thanks to the &quot;thought&quot; system. This allows you to fully immerse yourself in the story.</p></li></ul>",
